description: It is often difficult the remember all the foods and drinks you can consume on the Slow Carb Diet. A lot of times, we end up having to do searches on the internet. This is painful and inconvenient. Slow Carb Checker allows you to simply ask Alexa, for example, "can I have almond milk?" to find out.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Slow Carb Checker, can I eat apples?
Alexa, ask Slow Carb Checker, can I drink almond milk?
name: Slow Carb Checker
shortDescription: Allows users to find if if a certain food or drink can be consumed on the Slow Carb Diet
